## UE 5.7 MetaSound Node Enumeration APIs - Complete Reference

### PRIMARY API: INodeClassRegistry::IterateRegistry()
**Location:** `Engine/Plugins/Runtime/Metasound/Source/MetasoundFrontend/Public/MetasoundFrontendNodeClassRegistry.h`
**Include:** `#include "MetasoundFrontendNodeClassRegistry.h"`

**Function Signature:**
```cpp
virtual void IterateRegistry(
    FIterateMetasoundFrontendClassFunction InIterFunc, 
    EMetasoundFrontendClassType InClassType = EMetasoundFrontendClassType::Invalid
) const = 0;
```

**Callback Type:**
```cpp
using FIterateMetasoundFrontendClassFunction = TFunctionRef<void(const FMetasoundFrontendClass&)>;
```

**Usage Example:**
```cpp
auto& Registry = Metasound::Frontend::INodeClassRegistry::GetChecked();
Registry.IterateRegistry([](const FMetasoundFrontendClass& Class) {
    const FMetasoundFrontendClassMetadata& Metadata = Class.Metadata;
    FString ClassName = Metadata.ClassName.Name.ToString();
    FMetasoundFrontendVersionNumber Version = Metadata.Version;
    // Process Class...
});
```

**With Class Type Filter:**
```cpp
Registry.IterateRegistry(
    [](const FMetasoundFrontendClass& Class) {
        // Only classes matching EMetasoundFrontendClassType type will be passed
    },
    EMetasoundFrontendClassType::Node  // Filter by type
);
```

**Key Details:**
- Returns `INodeClassRegistry` instance via `INodeClassRegistry::Get()` or `INodeClassRegistry::GetChecked()`
- **Threading Warning:** The log in implementation warns that IterateRegistry is NOT thread-safe
- **Recommended Alternative:** Use `Metasound::Frontend::ISearchEngine` for thread-safe queries (see below)
- Implementation location: `MetasoundFrontend/Private/MetasoundFrontendNodeClassRegistry.cpp:1391`

### RECOMMENDED ALTERNATIVE: ISearchEngine
**Location:** `Engine/Plugins/Runtime/Metasound/Source/MetasoundFrontend/Public/MetasoundFrontendSearchEngine.h`
**Include:** `#include "MetasoundFrontendSearchEngine.h"`

**Primary Method for Runtime Discovery:**
```cpp
virtual TArray<FMetasoundFrontendClass> FindAllClasses(bool bInIncludeAllVersions) = 0;
```

**Usage:**
```cpp
auto& SearchEngine = Metasound::Frontend::ISearchEngine::Get();
SearchEngine.Prime();  // Cache queries for speed

TArray<FMetasoundFrontendClass> AllClasses = SearchEngine.FindAllClasses(
    false  // Only highest versions
);

for (const FMetasoundFrontendClass& Class : AllClasses) {
    const FMetasoundFrontendClassMetadata& Metadata = Class.Metadata;
    FString ClassName = Metadata.ClassName.Name.ToString();
    // Process...
}
```

**Additional ISearchEngine Methods:**
- `FindClassesWithName(const FMetasoundFrontendClassName& InName, bool bInSortByVersion)`
- `FindClassWithHighestVersion(const FMetasoundFrontendClassName& InName)`
- `FindAllInterfaces(bool bInIncludeAllVersions)`

### REGISTRY KEY STRUCTURE
**Type:** `FNodeClassRegistryKey` (defined in MetasoundFrontendRegistryKey.h)
**Contains:**
- `FMetasoundFrontendClassName ClassName` - Name + domain/namespace
- `FMetasoundFrontendVersionNumber Version` - Major/Minor version

### FRONTEND CLASS STRUCTURE
**Type:** `FMetasoundFrontendClass` (defined in MetasoundFrontendDocument.h)
**Key Fields:**
```cpp
struct FMetasoundFrontendClass {
    FMetasoundFrontendClassMetadata Metadata;  // ClassName, Version, Type
    FMetasoundFrontendInterface Interface;     // Inputs/Outputs pins
    // ... other fields
};
```

### CLASS TYPE ENUM
**Enum:** `EMetasoundFrontendClassType`
**Location:** MetasoundFrontendDocument.h
**Values:** Node, Interface, Graph, Variable, Input, Output, etc.

### C++ PLUGIN API PATH
For UE5 C++ plugin use:
```cpp
#include "MetasoundFrontendNodeClassRegistry.h"
#include "MetasoundFrontendSearchEngine.h"

// Get singleton
auto& Registry = Metasound::Frontend::INodeClassRegistry::GetChecked();
auto& SearchEngine = Metasound::Frontend::ISearchEngine::Get();
```

### KEY INCLUDES NEEDED
```cpp
#include "MetasoundFrontendNodeClassRegistry.h"     // INodeClassRegistry
#include "MetasoundFrontendSearchEngine.h"          // ISearchEngine (recommended)
#include "MetasoundFrontendDocument.h"              // FMetasoundFrontendClass, etc.
#include "MetasoundFrontendRegistryKey.h"           // FNodeClassRegistryKey
```

### BUILDER SUBSYSTEM ALTERNATIVE
**Location:** `MetasoundEngine/Public/MetasoundBuilderSubsystem.h`
**Type:** `UMetaSoundBuilderSubsystem`
- More limited - used for blueprint/runtime building, not enumeration
- Has methods: CreateSourceBuilder, CreatePatchBuilder
- Not recommended for node enumeration

### MASTER REGISTRY LOCATION
**Private Implementation:** `MetasoundFrontend/Private/MetasoundFrontendNodeClassRegistryPrivate.h`
**Registry Storage:**
```cpp
TMultiMap<FNodeClassRegistryKey, TSharedRef<INodeClassRegistryEntry, ESPMode::ThreadSafe>> RegisteredNodes;
```

### THREADING NOTES
- INodeClassRegistry::IterateRegistry() is NOT thread-safe (has explicit warning)
- ISearchEngine is thread-safe alternative with caching capability
- Use `ISearchEngine::Prime()` to pre-cache queries
